The Part Catalogue Package show the design elements around a parts evaluation and potential selection. The package that makes up the Part Catalogue contains:
  1. Part Inputs Canvas - a summary of the part with critical design aspects
  2. Parts Specs Package - Containing the Key Part Specification that are of interest to the design
  3. Parts Evaluation Canvas - which shows the pluses, deltas, gaps, and challenges based upon the initial part evaluation.
The %#NewCataloguePart#% Parts Specifications contains the package of specifications of the part that are relevant to the design inputs and design specifications.

This package has several diagrams that show the feedback of the for the part. The pluses or positive things that are being experienced now and the deltas or experiences that need to be eliminated or improved upon. <font color="#ff4500"> </font>
